# Workflow Decisions

The record of this project's tunable workflow settings. (Not `.claude/memory/decisions.md`, which records *architecture* decisions about the code.)

Change a setting with `/workflow-decisions` — it edits the live location **and** this record together. Each entry lists **Live in**, **Current**, and **Options**.

